SENATE BILL 853
C8, P5, S1 6lr2546
By: Senator Sydnor
Introduced and read first time: February 6, 2026
Assigned to: Education, Energy, and the Environment and Finance
A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Economic Development Activity – Nondisclosure Agreements
3 FOR the purpose of prohibiting certain individuals from entering into a nondisclosure
4 agreement with a person involved in an economic development activity, including
5 establishing or operating a data center; including public service companies as an
6 instrumentality of the State for the purpose of the Public Information Act; and
7 generally relating to economic development activity and the Public Information Act.
